  // if you have a compilation error here, your FPC trunk is too old
  // - TTypeData.AttributeTable was introduced in SVN 42356-42411 (2019/07)
  // -> undefine FPC_PROVIDE_ATTR_TABLE in Synopse.inc and recompile
